{"tid":630214,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（中二病+兵+後門狗+刷鞋仔）大唐毒撚","createTime":"2018-04-15T11:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T19:57:51.000Z","uid":63328,"like":53,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"26e726610f439c33ffad1307cfbeec305b6113aa","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/193446_4dc6adff7cce8286a7aed7137026e0da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F193446_4dc6adff7cce8286a7aed7137026e0da.jpg&h=1883a9b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唐玄宗先天元年（712），有個毒撚出世。佢好細個就死左老母，由姑母撫養長大。細個多病呀佢，佢同皇帝講自己<span style=\"color: pink;\"><em><strong>「少小多病，貧窮好學」。（《進封西嶽表》）</strong></em></span>係搏人同情定點，真係無人知。<br />\n<br />\n多得香港垃圾教育制度，我地對古人既認知通常都停留喺好悶同埋<strong>好撚悶</strong>。跳出個框框睇，可能佢係一隻病嬌，好似佢自稱：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>「七齡思即壯，開口詠鳳凰。九齡書大字，有作成一囊。」（〈壯遊〉）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/193129_96f26a0c9b20460a9e83dbba42626e3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F193129_96f26a0c9b20460a9e83dbba42626e3d.jpg&h=145639cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱，七歲就識作詩，九歲學寫字，仲有可以裝滿一個背囊既作品。表面睇好似好勁，但係實際就唔係。用香港既情況黎睇，七歲係小學二年班、九歲係四年班。佢四年班先學寫字，好可能連弱能人士都不如。<br />\n<br />\n去到十四五歲，佢既弱智程度加劇。佢自己話：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>「憶年十五心尚孩，健如黃犢走復來。庭前八月棗栗熟，一日上樹能千回。」（〈百憂集行〉）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一日上樹能千回？連登仔單手游出公海啦。十五歲？MK妹做左人阿婆啦。嗱我地睇人寫野要細心。<strong>十五歲健如黃犢</strong>？你岩岩先話自己細個多病咋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/194203_b80c9e4a3c7574dd218c273d3f7d02d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F194203_b80c9e4a3c7574dd218c273d3f7d02d2.jpg&h=e3e18ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔單止咁，我估喱種人無咩朋友。又係佢自己話：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">「性豪業嗜酒，嫉惡懷剛腸。脫落小時輩，結交皆老蒼。」（〈壯遊〉）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n十四五歲，開始扮大人，扮中意飲酒，係正常既。不過「嫉惡懷剛腸」，即係正義撚、報警撚啦，實在不可以饒恕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/193706_47a7a539e3c696a9a5b3f1234d711ecf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F193706_47a7a539e3c696a9a5b3f1234d711ecf.jpg&h=ca12a593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗咁上下年紀既人，好可能集體杯葛佢，所以佢既朋友都係六七十路以上。<br />\n<br />\n禍不單行，佢仲有少少中二。又係佢話：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>「往昔十四五，出遊翰墨場。斯文崔（尚）魏（啟心）徒，以我似班（固）揚（雄）。」（〈壯遊〉）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n讚佢既崔尚，係武則天久視二年（701）進士，大中大夫，行尚書祠部郎中。魏啟心，則係中宗神龍三年（707）進士。當時崔尚係鄭州刺史，魏啟心係豫州刺史。都唔算係細官啦。不過咁，喱件事有無令你諗起一個人？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/192543_0d6f6dbefe42ccd6a502f7778978c046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F192543_0d6f6dbefe42ccd6a502f7778978c046.jpg&h=0dacceed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">張如城在2000年的廣東省吳川市中國五四青年運動節歌唱比賽，被中國市府人員邀請做表演嘉賓，獲市委書記和公安局長頒發《最佳榮譽獎》和《最佳勇氣獎》，被稱為「亞洲神童」及「亞洲最年輕音樂創作人」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大唐鄭州刺史+豫州刺史 VS 本朝廣東省吳川市市委書記+公安局長<br />\n<br />\n似班固、揚雄 VS「亞洲神童」、「亞洲最年輕音樂創作人」<br />\n<br />\n你覺得邊個勁？好明顯，喺十五歲黎講，張如城完勝。"},{"pid":"d5487642839d3a08f6747dd65c2f3a8470ab842a","tid":630214,"uid":334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T11:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4978666113c64f1671c980186736dc203c6c51f3","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T11:47:31.000Z","msg":"畀畀面，幫我刷下存在感，睇完就畀個正/負皮。<br />\n<br />\n100%唔保證會寫完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febc4466420e15a9006f4eb3cf2c6062d719224a","tid":630214,"uid":83444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T12:13:50.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb85127943925489d2cb1e556efef483db915414","tid":630214,"uid":13841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3124f2b6f7dd2d57b7a95894c2cbb512a8296cde","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb85127943925489d2cb1e556efef483db915414","tid":630214,"uid":13841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:34:42.000Z","msg":"成日見到你推po,  多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb044f084677e4db92f342db4338eac3ac0306fd","tid":630214,"uid":6221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e825c219ce69b63e7cef338ef274b7080219f9","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:10:15.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"540c5f730a6dfe57a284daad552a610331607863","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:25:44.000Z","msg":"畀我推到第二頁"},{"pid":"6fb76f114f7b80a33996faa03c8d447d887a87f0","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:39:56.000Z","msg":"大唐毒撚．二．考試炒粉搵老豆，作詩無計問阿爺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/012652_5211795e662fd86159ef7d88d0e1f524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F012652_5211795e662fd86159ef7d88d0e1f524.jpg&h=1d7cc45c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先觀摩一下日本成人禮。<br />\n<br />\n古代男性二十歲行冠禮，表示成人。大約喺開元十九年（731），二十歲既毒撚無野做開始做周圍去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">「浪跡於筆下豐草長林，實自弱冠之年。」（《進三大禮賦表》）</span><br />\n<br />\n可以肯定既，係佢曾經去過吳越，仲差啲去埋日本：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">東下姑蘇臺，已具浮海航。到今有遺恨，不得窮扶桑。<br />\n王謝風流遠，闔廬丘墓荒。劍池石壁仄，長洲荷芰香。<br />\n嵯峨閶門北，清廟映回塘。每趨吳太伯，撫事淚浪浪。<br />\n蒸魚聞匕首，除道哂要章。枕戈憶勾踐，渡浙想秦皇。<br />\n越女天下白，鑒湖五月涼。剡溪蘊秀異，欲罷不能忘。（〈壯遊〉）</span><br />\n<br />\n姑蘇係現今蘇州，扶桑就即係日本啦。可以想像曾經有一班前往日本既船喺佢面前出現，但係佢無好好珍惜，等到失去既時候，先後悔莫及。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/012827_415c1c64558231b4d577ee776cf0fb61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F012827_415c1c64558231b4d577ee776cf0fb61.png&h=3cae5ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，佢唔去日本可能係要供樓呢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於闔廬丘、劍池、長洲、閶門、清廟，都不外乎係啲地方名，全部喺蘇州；吳太伯、專諸匕首、朱買臣除道，都係啲出自吳越既典故。我認為哩首詩既記事價值大於文學價值，所以都係唔多講啦。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n開元二十三年（735），二十四歲，喱一年佢離開吳越，去到東都洛陽參加進士考試。<br />\n<br />\n年輕人總是天真，佢覺得自己同屈原、賈誼差唔多，至少都勁過曹植、劉楨。考試之前，梗係覺得自己勁。考試之後，就梗係收皮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">歸帆拂天姥，中歲貢舊鄉。氣劘屈賈壘，目短曹劉牆。<br />\n忤下考功第，獨辭京尹堂。（〈壯遊〉）</span><br />\n<br />\n延申閱讀：〈高考放榜前後分析潮文〉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E6%94%BE%E6%A6%9C%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A6%259C%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259E%2590%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E6%2596%2587&d=ZwCjmBT0kzfAd9fKNb%2F40%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f90e9043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E6%94%BE%E6%A6%9C%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87</a><br />\n<br />\n無論點都好，嗰一年，佢考唔到。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n靠父幹，中國人玩左幾千年啦，你估而家先有？Come on James，唔好咁天真啦。考試失敗，佢繼續佢既trip。今次由洛陽向東行，即係齊、趙之旅（今山東河北）。<br />\n<br />\nWhy ？考試失敗，佢要搵Daddy抱抱呱。當時佢老豆喺兗州做司馬。（有無打三國志既讀者？洛陽向東進係陳留/ 許昌，曹操就係喺兗州起家。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/013026_a9ac1cc9410a5d04c9ec63f2808e87f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F013026_a9ac1cc9410a5d04c9ec63f2808e87f5.jpg&h=42aa5b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（Google search 返黎既兗州城）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n犀利啦，哩隻野去到兗州，寫左首詩叫做〈登兗州城樓〉，好可能係佢人生第一首律詩。人地做人，可以靠父幹。哩條粉腸，作詩係靠爺幹。睇睇佢首詩：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">〈登兗州城樓〉<br />\n東郡趨庭日，南樓縱目初。<br />\n浮雲連海岱，平野入青徐。<br />\n孤嶂秦碑在，荒城魯殿餘。<br />\n從來多古意，臨眺獨躊躇。</div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首聯點題，寫自己去到東郡，登上南樓睇風景。<br />\n<br />\n第二句「縱目」引出頷聯、頸聯，即其眼前所見。<br />\n<br />\n尾聯「躊躇」感懷，又由頸聯古蹟引出。<br />\n<br />\n末句「臨眺」又與首句「縱目」相呼應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哩啲咪叫章法囉。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不過，係抄佢阿爺既。睇睇佢阿爺首詩：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">〈登襄陽樓〉<br />\n旅客三秋至，層城四望開。<br />\n楚山橫地出，漢水接天回。<br />\n冠蓋非新里，章華即舊臺。<br />\n習池風景異，歸路滿塵埃。</div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n對照兩首詩既結構，阿爺首聯點題登樓，個孫又係咁做。<br />\n<br />\n阿爺用「四望」，引出中間兩聯景物；而個孫則照辦煮碗用「縱目」。<br />\n<br />\n阿爺中間兩聯寫景，個孫又係。<br />\n<br />\n阿爺頷聯寫自然景物，頸聯寫古蹟，個孫又係。<br />\n<br />\n阿爺頷聯用長鏡頭寫大景、遠景，頸聯用短鏡頭寫小景、近景。個孫又係。<br />\n<br />\n只係尾聯少少唔同。阿爺話「風景異」抒發物在人非之感，而個孫就直接話「臨眺獨躊躇」。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n又話自己同屈原、賈誼同級既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毒撚廿四歲人成就列表：<br />\n<br />\n(1) 問屋企攞錢去旅行<br />\n(2) 去唔成日本<br />\n(3) 公開試失敗<br />\n(4) 讀書唔得，投靠老豆<br />\n(5) 學人寫詩，執阿爺口水尾"},{"pid":"23f2e898ccd97a47d42e5277078453734507ec56","tid":630214,"uid":41957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"終於見到post2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有埋圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924134d7e9aa2ae9c1fec421f92d856ed7215fe7","tid":630214,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf5e41f5308a3f86e7564f7576dec063eb96dfb","tid":630214,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打用另一個角度寫大詩人<br />\n有趣，期待後文！<br />\n不過似乎有排寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e30b7d82d8f417af4b258b49df4cd58580175b","tid":630214,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"幾有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d559ecffd54e712d970b49c6b1956ef23c52d9a3","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adf5e41f5308a3f86e7564f7576dec063eb96dfb","tid":630214,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打用另一個角度寫大詩人<br />\n有趣，期待後文！<br />\n不過似乎有排寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"寫到2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d78ae9207b47a0361331d3bb27d6c4e851fb5cb","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"e682c971be7a2ced6287c0cab9655cb68203b8cb","tid":630214,"uid":61075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a329953319f81678e6c271c2ecb9de4a3a35d8b","tid":630214,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:54:31.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a307a615600e7f2a8db5c1ce35c5951c12a25f1","tid":630214,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"來啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b431eef2cb0e33c566ef769f5cb726674f5559b5","tid":630214,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T19:28:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c18eba5d026e403e8c7184480a4a55d6585e60df","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:36:32.000Z","msg":"喱個禮拜無，下個禮拜先。等唔到就叫次雞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/516629/page/8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/516629/page/8</a>"},{"pid":"c664854f744ccff1f294540b48b89ecc54f1d5da","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"推一下姐，無文既"},{"pid":"50022fcb9116885984344e48f23bb801177b4f6c","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"哩個禮拜會出一篇"},{"pid":"8dc33b6d11b06cb138a7cea596c27f1faed6716e","tid":630214,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50022fcb9116885984344e48f23bb801177b4f6c","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"哩個禮拜會出一篇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12134badd35c34fde1acb1dfee3ebf5950899e7","tid":630214,"uid":83444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0e239def2905670691bc9c0d0ca1b1deb981f180","tid":630214,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"48b49ca379ae3178800f277c9a27f9f3dc796d9e","tid":630214,"uid":47783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:45:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ad6b42dd29005e59b87a348af7fde664a397f58c","tid":630214,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老味好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d36a0e836389f894a70e5701cb77b08e5451c6","tid":630214,"uid":159669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T07:53:44.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"4d98256f90dcf844efab157f53e127ee60485bac","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"大唐毒撚．三．我要玩到30歲！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/121616_d9adf137d1bf35dc6622c28ab77ceeba.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F121616_d9adf137d1bf35dc6622c28ab77ceeba.jpeg&h=fd71dec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n射飛曾縱鞚，引臂落鶖鶬。佢係一個神射手。<br />\n<br />\n上回提到，二十四歲既毒撚公開試失敗之後，開始佢既頹廢人生。正常人既gap year 都係一年，多既就兩年。佢就&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/121700_5d2c2e2e14a6d902fc2edfcb95600b47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F121700_5d2c2e2e14a6d902fc2edfcb95600b47.jpg&h=ef9130c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哩啲叫：呼鷹皂櫪林，逐獸雲雪岡。source：mon hunt<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">放蕩齊趙間，裘馬頗清狂。春歌叢臺[1]上，冬獵青丘[2]旁。<br />\n呼鷹皂櫪林[3]，逐獸雲雪岡[4]。射飛[5]曾縱鞚[6]，引臂落鶖鶬。<br />\n蘇侯[7]據鞍喜，忽如攜葛強[8]。快意八九年，西歸到咸陽。 《壯遊》</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[1] 叢臺：於河北邯鄲內<br />\n[2] 青丘：山東地方<br />\n[3]、[4] ：齊地名<br />\n[5]、[6]：射飛鳥、縱馬<br />\n[7] ：蘇源明。路人甲，下場係餓死<br />\n[8] ：葛強，晉代將領<br />\n<br />\n首詩大概係講佢春天唱歌、冬天狩獵，成日踐踏花花草草，追殺弱小動物。不過，快意八九年，又係假既。玩左大約六、七年啦，去到三十歲左右，齊、趙既自然環境就被佢破壞哂。"},{"pid":"6da8b529c28c3e942d3fd9313cd508fff4ac18d5","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:22:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩講過，毒撚去過好多唔同地方，殺害左好多小動物。喱個過程奠定左佢寫物寫景既基礎。講埋喱首：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">〈望嶽〉<br />\n岱宗夫如何？齊魯青未了。<br />\n造化鍾神秀，陰陽割昏曉。<br />\n盪胸生層雲，決眥入歸鳥。<br />\n會當凌絕頂，一覽眾山小。</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n中學讀哩首詩，覺得首聯好霸氣。<br />\n<br />\n岱宗，即係泰山。但係唔講泰山，用別名。<br />\n<br />\n岱，即係山。宗，即係最大嗰個。<br />\n<br />\n泰山背後既意蘊係咩？秦始、漢武封禪既地方，夠唔夠大？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/121827_d311c94958c47230ffbf093c58991b51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F121827_d311c94958c47230ffbf093c58991b51.jpg&h=fd95b282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">羅嘉良做秦始皇無得頂。</span><br />\n<br />\n齊魯，即係山東。青未了，睇到最盡，全部都係青色。<br />\n<br />\n唔同你講幾大，佢同你講全部都係青色，由齊到魯睇到盡，都係泰山既青色，夠大未？<br />\n<br />\n「岱宗夫如何？齊魯青未了。」<br />\n<br />\n即係：「知唔知咩叫山中霸皇呀？大到你睇唔哂呀，全部都係綠色呀，睇到幾遠都係綠色呀」<br />\n<br />\n(有無去過santorini 既讀者？當我睇見愛琴海同愛琴海的天空時，海天交融無盡既藍色令我領略到咩叫「未了」。)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/122044_866256e8c105d32b78185234cb0a5176.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F122044_866256e8c105d32b78185234cb0a5176.png&h=e2170302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上人士既綠色可能大過泰山。<br />\n<br />\n頜聯學習下煉字。「造化鍾神秀，陰陽割昏曉。」<br />\n<br />\n鍾，解「倒落去」，聚集。泰山靚成點？靚到好似倒落去咁。<br />\n<br />\n割，解分開。仲有幾誇張？日落既時候，一邊光、一邊暗。<br />\n最後兩聯：「盪胸生層雲，決眥入歸鳥。會當凌絕頂，一覽眾山小。」<br />\n<br />\n望住一片片白雲在天上舒卷，又有飛鳥乘著暮色歸巢，令我好想上山頂睇下，世界係幾咁渺少。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺唔覺得有唔妥？<br />\n你覺唔覺得有唔妥？<br />\n你覺唔覺得有唔妥？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母！「會當凌絕頂」，原來你無上過泰山？<br />\n<br />\n個人認為全詩中，「盪胸生層雲，決眥入歸鳥」比較遜色，原因係佢ff 出黎。"},{"pid":"1965e8e44222a38d9c6fef916416df729bab22d3","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"講多首。<br />\n<br />\n真係唔好意思。毒撚憂國憂民既蓋棺論定，只係中學教育送畀你既偏見。事實上，佢30歲前，周圍去旅行，周圍開party，國家大事，都係等國家仆街再算啦。以下喱首詩，同樣係齊、趙之旅途中寫既：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">〈夜宴左氏莊〉<br />\n林風纖月落，衣露淨琴張。<br />\n暗水流花徑，春星帶草堂。<br />\n檢書燒燭短，看劍引杯長。<br />\n詩罷聞吳詠，扁舟意不忘。</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/122336_8dedccc93ebc3d1e91c27086ad78bdad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F122336_8dedccc93ebc3d1e91c27086ad78bdad.jpg&h=2e34a10e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幻想：<br />\n微微既林風吹拂，吹送著微微帶有草木滋潤的空氣。彎彎既新月慢慢落下，隨著春夜的露水逐漸凝固，開展了琴聲。<br />\n小溪流水落花，春星熣爛，天上人間。<br />\n<br />\n轉入去左氏莊，一班人讀書飲酒，就要襯喱個時候。忽然聽到有人用吳音吟詠，又勾起幾年前泛舟江南的回憶。唉，我又想去江南旅行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n就係咁，佢30歲。下一集佢就將會轉向人生既新污點。面臨被杯葛同鄙視既人生。<br />\n<br />\n如果我會寫的話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa36048b7efe0a352e5dd7fb53ff7a803ed2be1","tid":630214,"uid":83444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1cf67e87e7326cec333dda5aa510ba7cd99961","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T17:54:54.000Z","msg":"排版會唔會唔好睇?"},{"pid":"e9aa03f0ccce25bf41f1029dbb9369e8fcee587f","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:18:14.000Z","msg":"定係無人睇?"},{"pid":"cb9b47fd491921c12ac627a978f9f657dc397b61","tid":630214,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1cf67e87e7326cec333dda5aa510ba7cd99961","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T17:54:54.000Z","msg":"排版會唔會唔好睇?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"好咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c58daf60f7e7716abe70886953f6da369201aa7","tid":630214,"uid":61680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"留名等開估<br />\n<br />\n雖然Google十成會即刻揾到，不過都係等樓主揭盅過癮過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8678ba56ebfa5bd7209c350486101cc128e890af","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c58daf60f7e7716abe70886953f6da369201aa7","tid":630214,"uid":61680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"留名等開估<br />\n<br />\n雖然Google十成會即刻揾到，不過都係等樓主揭盅過癮過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"好奇一問，巴打係真唔知定假唔知？"},{"pid":"2a4a8cb88ef0b6d93daefca156a42c503343f510","tid":630214,"uid":61680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8678ba56ebfa5bd7209c350486101cc128e890af","tid":630214,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c58daf60f7e7716abe70886953f6d